author: Cleo Abram
description:
What happens when an asteroid hits the earth? It’s NOT like a bullet hitting a wall!

An asteroid is going SO MUCH FASTER that when it hits, that hunk of rock or metal immediately turns from a solid into superheated gas… 

So if an asteroid were headed for Earth, what could we DO about it? 

Turns out, we have 5 options…

To find out what they are, subscribe!

#shorts #science #asteroid #explosion #earth
title: What REALLY Happens If This Asteroid Hits Earth
